window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>\"It’s the only logical strategy…<br> <br> …and the Commonwealth has a plan to counter it.<br> <br> Does he have the allies to win?<br> <br> Alistair knows the risks, but he must take the Ice Queen’s military and the gigante to Planet Phoenix. In order to defeat the Ascendant, Alexander de Finita, and put this nightmare behind him, it’ll take every asset he can bring together.<br> <br> There’s just one problem.<br> <br> The Commonwealth plans to strike first.<br> <br> If they control the star-gate at Phoenix, all is lost.<br> <br> Every choice he’s made has had consequences, but none as gave as Alistair’s next move. The Ascendant has the positional advantage. Should Alistair protect his pieces, make a sacrifice, or play a gambit?<br> <br> In this chess game…<br> <br> …the future is on the line.<br> <br> Performed by Terence Aselford, Danny Gavigan, Bradley Foster Smith, Zeke Alton, Keith Richards, Chris Stinson, Christopher Williams, Lydia Kraniotis, Marni Penning, Rob McFadyen, Andy Clemence, Eric Messner, Michael John Casey, Tyler Hyrchuk, Nanette Savard, Amanda Forstrom, David Jourdan, Terence Aselford, Tia Shearer, Mark Harrietha, Peter Holdway, Scott McCormick, Nora Achrati, Thomas Penny, Wyn Delano, Colleen Delany, Richard Rohan, Mike Ciporkin, James Konicek, Karen Novack, Torian Brackett, Nicole Perez, and Yasmin Tuazon.\"</p>"; 
